HEADWORD: Superfecundation
<hw>Su`per*fec`un*da"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>Fertilization of two ova, at the same
menstruation, by two different acts of coition.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superfecundity</ent>⟦br⟧
